articles.title: Post Game Report - Division 6: Hellfish v Hat Trick Swayzes
articles.content:
Division 6 - Hat Trick Swayzes overtook Hellfish 5 - 2. For Hat Trick Swayzes, David Di Rico tallied 2 Goals, 1 Assist, 3 Points. Paul Sobansky had the scorekeeper working with 1 Goal, 1 Point. Leighton Scheer wowed the crowd with 1 Goal, 1 Point. David Di Rico got 1st Star. Thomas Henry wowed the crowd with 1 Goal, 1 Assist, 2 Points. For Hellfish, Lukas Papik broke out 24 Saves. Ulisses Machado wowed the crowd with 2 Goals, 2 Points. Visit the game page at: http://icehq.hockeysyte.com/game/6026

Catch the Replay on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZcYzG29ONSQ
